# Billing Rules

## Stripe Integration
- Use `stripe` npm package with latest API version
- Always use Checkout Sessions for payment
- Always handle webhooks for subscription state
- Store: customer_id, subscription_status
- Never store card details

## Pricing
- Free: limited requests
- Pro: €19–€49/month (subscription)

## Flow
landing → checkout → access

## Webhook Events to Handle
- checkout.session.completed
- customer.subscription.created
- customer.subscription.updated
- customer.subscription.deleted
- invoice.payment_failed

## Business Rule
- Charge early, even if product incomplete
- Validate willingness to pay first
